{"tid":1501430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日機場 唔好講咁多","createTime":"2019-08-24T10:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T06:08:08.000Z","uid":302,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8e5b32bbce0dce74512577d649e71d326ffd626f","tid":1501430,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:58:34.000Z","msg":"街頭抗爭 又比人打爆眼又比人拉<br />\n機場 又可以直爆春袋 又可以冷氣底下抗爭 <br />\n仲犧牲唔夠？<br />\n<br />\n係街頭 一係就變海嘯浸死班狗 但事實係做潮退多<br />\n中途仲要損兵折將 對政府既消耗又唔大 其他市民又who fucking cares咁<br />\n既然打唔贏班狗 又想直接消耗政府 重申一次 機場<br />\n聽日見！"},{"pid":"e8d6d3439e7e0339b82ced4cca65e0c93c700a5f","tid":1501430,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:06:54.000Z","msg":"禮拜五人鏈 禮拜六街頭 禮拜日機場 <br />\n一至四不合佢運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36450de992255dd9a25d5813020c07de289a8722","tid":1501430,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:08:06.000Z","msg":"唔好臨時改行程<br />\n我會照去葵涌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4f86cecd8029cb1e0e10b829352475a1234097","tid":1501430,"uid":168960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:15:06.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"94ab818bdad0beb5ae00a57de8b92afa2083754c","tid":1501430,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36450de992255dd9a25d5813020c07de289a8722","tid":1501430,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:08:06.000Z","msg":"唔好臨時改行程<br />\n我會照去葵涌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:22:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">兩邊都去</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地要長時間塞<br />\n就要keep 住一車車巴士地鐵無間斷流入機場<br />\n<br />\n朝早塞完比人趕返出黎嘅 下午剛好可以遊行<br />\n遊行行到終點就一齊去機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本聽日荃葵青就係天意！<br />\n仲有邊區入機場有咁撚方便？！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRecap:<br />\n<br />\n方案一：<br />\n朝早入機場嘅人下午去遊行<br />\n方案二：<br />\n下午遊行嘅人遊完去機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n流水式集會2.0 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入機場原因：<br />\n<br />\n我而家搵到個制衡狗隊濫暴方法<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n[班勇武手足可能一直都去錯地方] 聽朝還眼楂緊政府春袋集會!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5bf5bd75e4ee3f15a38841caf6f7e17b73f90a2","tid":1501430,"uid":272686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:34:54.000Z","msg":"大家加油<br />\n要揸實呢個春袋"},{"pid":"7eea01ca04cb21666603cc10a7786132d48aa323","tid":1501430,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲post又沉"},{"pid":"8302f465a25e07868f565c80e94fdb6c098cc4d0","tid":1501430,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"expressive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}